  "prompt": "What hotel in Patna would be safe for unmarried couples, without the harassment of police, hotel staff, and moral police?",
  "response": "When searching for a hotel in Patna that offers a safe and comfortable stay for unmarried couples, consider looking for establishments known for their respectful and professional service. Here are a few options to consider:\n\n1. **Lemon Tree Premier Patna**: Known for its professional staff and good amenities, this hotel generally offers a safe environment for all guests including couples.\n\n2. **Hotel The Panache**: Located at a prime location, this hotel is reputed for its courteous staff and modern facilities.\n\n3. **Hotel Maurya**: One of the oldest and most reputed hotels in Patna, it is well-regarded for its hospitality and service standards.\n\n4. **Hotel Patliputra Exotica**: With good reviews for its service and environment, this hotel is also a viable option for unmarried couples.\n\n5. **FabHotel Sangam International**: FabHotels are generally known for their professional service and this branch in Patna is no exception.\n\nTo ensure a hassle-free experience:\n- It's advisable to always carry valid ID proof.\n- Opt for hotels that have a clear policy around serving all guests without discrimination.\n- It\u2019s often helpful to make the booking through reputable travel websites that highlight couple-friendly hotels.\n\nWhile these options should mitigate concerns around police or moral harassment, always make discrete inquiries at the time of booking to make sure the hotel policies align with your needs.",
